The '''JK series droid''' was a series of [[Security droid/Legends|security droids]] produced on [[Ord Cestus/Legends|Ord Cestus]], nicknamed '''''Jedi Killers''''' by [[Smuggler/Legends|smugglers]] because they had famously been able to [[Death/Legends|kill]] [[Jedi/Legends|Jedi]]. The most famous product in this series was the [[JK-13]].

